Class DIntNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs463lab7.DIntNode
  • public class DIntNode
extends java.lang.Object
    DIntNode.java A DIntNode provides a node for a doubly linked list with integer data in each node. Lists of nodes can be made of any length, limited only by the amount of free memory in the heap. But beyond Integer.MAX_VALUE
